Jaffrey, Edna Lewis even.

00:08:02.020 --> 00:08:06.430
You could consider her to be an
expat I think from the South.

00:08:06.430 --> 00:08:10.930
You know they're people whose
motivation to write about food

00:08:10.930 --> 00:08:17.100
