was born out of nostalgia in a way

00:08:17.100 --> 00:08:21.850
like they wanted to explore
something that they really missed.

00:08:21.850 --> 00:08:23.290
And that seems the same for you.

00:08:23.290 --> 00:08:26.990
So when you're in Texas, like how
do think that affected your outlook

00:08:26.990 --> 00:08:29.940
on cooking, you know, being exposed

00:08:29.940 --> 00:08:32.600
to the Mexican food
in Texas particularly?

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:34.850
&gt;&gt; Pati Janich: I love
that question, Joe.

00:08:34.850 --> 00:08:36.150
I love Joe.

00:08:36.150 --> 00:08:37.450
&gt;&gt; Joe Yonana: [Laughs].

00:08:37.450 --> 00:08:38.750
&gt;&gt; Pati Janich: It
