00:08:40.050 --> 00:08:41.350
You guys -- .

00:08:41.350 --> 00:08:42.650
&gt;&gt; Pati Janich: Yeah.

00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:43.950
We just, yeah.

00:08:43.950 --> 00:08:45.250
I think it is so true.

00:08:45.250 --> 00:08:47.150
Distance does so much to you.

00:08:47.150 --> 00:08:50.570
I mean many fabulous
writers about, you know,

00:08:50.570 --> 00:08:53.370
Mexican history writers
