00:09:14.770 --> 00:09:18.300
And I feel that happened
to me when I left to Texas.

00:09:18.300 --> 00:09:25.880
And it was many, I think it's that
constant pair that I feel that is

00:09:25.880 --> 00:09:29.550
at the same time painful and
at the same time beautiful.

00:09:29.550 --> 00:09:30.940
You know, I always like to say

00:09:30.940 --> 00:09:34.110
