eyes water with the American anthem.

00:09:55.130 --> 00:09:57.350
And I love the U.S., you know.

00:09:57.350 --> 00:09:59.040
I'm so grateful for America.

00:09:59.040 --> 00:10:03.450
And at the same time I've learned
so much about the United States,

00:10:03.450 --> 00:10:05.850
things that I thought
I knew as a Mexican,

00:10:05.850 --> 00:10:08.060
