00:11:45.570 --> 00:11:46.870
&gt;&gt; Joe Yonana: Oh, that's painful.

00:11:46.870 --> 00:11:48.170
Yeah.

00:11:48.170 --> 00:11:50.260
&gt;&gt; Pati Jinich: And
it was really painful.

