00:40:21.570 --> 00:40:23.570
It's like toasty.

00:40:23.570 --> 00:40:24.870
&gt;&gt; Joe Yonana: Like nutty?

00:40:24.870 --> 00:40:26.320
Nutty.

00:40:26.320 --> 00:40:27.620
&gt;&gt; Pati Jinich: Yeah.

